import pandas as pd
import xarray as xr

        self.right = pd.Timestamp(right)
        self.closed = closed

class MockCalendar:
    def __init__(self, anchor, length):
        self.anchor = anchor
        self.length = length

        return pd.Series([MockInterval('2019-07-04', '2019-12-31'),

    print("✓ Calendar info added to dataset attrs successfully")
